(78, 1, '2016-06-13 00:40:32', '2016-06-12 16:40:32', '{:zh}<p>宇部兴产机械（上海）有限公司将参展2016年4月15日(周五)～4月17日(周日)、在中国宁波市召开的『第7届宁波国际铸造锻造压铸工业展览会』、特此告知。<br />\r\n       本次宁波展会是以压铸设备制造为主体的展示会。<br />\r\n       展会中将展示由中国生产制造的小型机UB350iC机型，并介绍小型、中型iC系列机型、中型iS2系列机型、 大型iV系列机型、UBE压铸成形技术。<br />\r\n       期待您的莅临！</p>\r\n<p>        【展会概要】<br />\r\n・时间：2016年4月15日(周五)～4月17日(周日)<br />\r\n・地址：宁波国际会议中心3号馆[地址：宁波会展路181号]<br />\r\n・主办方：宁波市经济与信息化委员会<br />\r\n・展示内容：①实体机展示　UB350iC(本体＋給汤机)<br />\r\n                  ② USH介绍录像放映<br />\r\n                  ③操作展示<br />\r\n・USH、UBE集团介绍<br />\r\n   ・小型Sh3系列机型、小型・中型iC系列机型、<br />\r\n     中型iS2系列机型、大型iV系列机型介绍<br />\r\n   ・ADSTEFAN介绍 UB350iCUB350iC</p>{:}{:en}Ube Xing production machinery (Shanghai) Co., Ltd. will participate in the 2016 on 15 April (Friday) to April 17 (Sunday), held in Ningbo, China, "the 7th Ningbo International Foundry Casting Forging Industry Exhibition", we are pleased to inform you.\r\nThe Ningbo exhibition is to die casting equipment manufacturing as the main display.\r\nExposition will display manufactured by the Chinese production of minicomputer UB350iC models, and the small and medium-sized IC series models, medium-sized iS2 series models, large IV series models, Ube die casting forming technology.\r\nLook forward to your visit!\r\n[exhibition summary]\r\nTime: April 15, 2016 (Friday), April 17th (Sunday)\r\nAddress: Ningbo International Conference Center, No. 3, No. 181 Exhibition Road, Ningbo, No.\r\nSponsor: Ningbo economic and Information Technology Committee\r\nDisplay the contents of the contents of the display: a physical machine display UB350iC (ontology + soup machine)\r\nUSH introduction video show\r\nOperation display\r\nUBE, USH Group Introduction\r\nSh3 small iC series models, small and medium size series models,\r\nMedium iS2 series models, large iV series models introduced\r\nADSTEFAN introduction to UB350iCUB350iC{:}', '{:zh}第七届宁波国际铸造锻造压铸工业展览会 展会介绍{:}{:en}Introduction of the seventh Ningbo international casting and Forging Die Casting Industry Exhibition{:}', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '%e7%ac%ac%e4%b8%83%e5%b1%8a%e5%ae%81%e6%b3%a2%e5%9b%bd%e9%99%85%e9%93%b8%e9%80%a0%e9%94%bb%e9%80%a0%e5%8e%8b%e9%93%b8%e5%b7%a5%e4%b8%9a%e5%b1%95%e8%a7%88%e4%bc%9a-%e5%b1%95%e4%bc%9a%e4%bb%8b%e7%bb%8d', '', '', '2016-06-23 21:44:08', '2016-06-23 13:44:08', '', 0, 'http://localhost/jb_wordpress/?p=78', 0, 'post', '', 0),
